V0209_01_00_00_0.text: Let me see how you Duel!

V0209_01_00_01_0.text: Victory is impossible until you overcome your limitations!

V0209_01_00_02_0.text: I'll show you a strategy that you've never seen before!

V0209_01_00_03_0.text: Can you find the Synchro Solution?

V0209_01_00_04_0.text: Yusei, you'll never defeat me until you exceed your limits!

V0209_01_00_05_0.text: My mission is to protect Yusei from every threat!

V0209_01_00_06_0.text:
Are you scared of me?
That's expected.

V0209_01_00_06_1.text: Since I was sent here to stop you from achieving your goal!

V0209_01_00_07_0.text: I'll take you on in this Duel!

V0209_01_00_07_1.text: Fall victim to my Accel Synchro!

V0209_01_00_08_0.text: I don't need to tell you who I am since you'll soon be gone!

V0209_01_00_09_0.text: I will save my allies - and save you as well!

V0209_03_00_00_0.text: You should think of a new strategy if you want to win!

V0209_03_00_05_0.text: About time you're taking this Duel seriously.

V0209_05_00_00_0.text: With this draw, I'll show you what lies beyond the future!

V0209_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0209_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I set!

V0209_08_00_00_0.text:
I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
TGX1-HL!

V0209_08_00_00_1.text: I halve a T.G.'s ATK and DEF to destroy a Spell or Trap!

V0209_08_00_01_0.text:
I activate my Continuous Spell!
TGX300!

V0209_08_00_02_1.text: I Special Summon a T.G. Synchro Monster from my Graveyard!

V0209_08_00_03_1.text: I return 3 T.G. in my Graveyard to my deck to draw 2 cards!

V0209_08_00_04_1.text: I swap control of my T.G. with your monster!

V0209_08_00_05_0.text: You think that will work against me?

V0209_08_00_05_1.text: I activate the Trap Card, Sonic Stun!

V0209_08_00_06_0.text:
I activate my Counter Trap!
Gravity Collapse!

V0209_08_00_06_1.text: It stops you from summoning a monster and destroys it!

V0209_08_00_07_0.text: I activate my Trap Card, Tuner Capture!

V0209_08_00_07_1.text: I Special Summon a Tuner from your Graveyard on to my field!

V0209_08_00_08_0.text: I activate my Trap, Synchro Material!

V0209_08_00_08_1.text: I can use your monster to Synchro Summon this turn!

V0209_08_00_09_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Urgent Tuning!

V0209_08_00_09_1.text: It lets me Synchro Summon a Synchro Monster!

V0209_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Compulsory Evacuation Device!

V0209_08_00_10_1.text: I return a monster on the field to the hand!

V0209_09_00_01_0.text: When Buster Blaster is equipped, its effect activates!

V0209_09_00_02_0.text: Due to Booster Raptor's effect, I add a T.G. to my hand!

V0209_09_00_03_0.text: When all my monsters are T.G., I can Special Summon this!

V0209_09_00_04_0.text:
Drill Fish's effect activates!
I destroy your monster!

V0209_09_00_06_0.text: Due to Cyber Magician, I add a T.G. in my deck to my hand!

V0209_09_00_07_0.text: By lowering my T.G.'s ATK, I can Special Summon this card!

V0209_09_00_08_0.text: When a monster is destroyed, I can Special Summon this card!

V0209_09_00_09_0.text: T.G. Striker lets me add a T.G. in my deck to my hand!

V0209_09_00_10_0.text: Catapult Dragon Special Summons a T.G. Tuner!

V0209_09_00_11_0.text: Since this monster was Level 4 or lower, I can summon this!

V0209_09_00_12_0.text: T.G. Warwolf adds another monster in my deck to my hand!

V0209_09_00_13_0.text: By Synchro Summoning, Jet Falcon's effect activates!

V0209_09_00_14_0.text: Rush Rhino adds another monster in my deck to my hand!

V0209_09_00_15_1.text: I Special Summon a Level 4 or lower T.G. from my Graveyard!

V0209_09_00_16_0.text: Screw Serpent's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0209_09_00_18_0.text: Wonder Magician can destroy a Spell or a Trap!

V0209_09_00_19_0.text: Watch as I unlock the true power of Synchro Summoning!

V0209_09_00_20_0.text: When Wonder Magician is destroyed, I draw a card!

V0209_09_00_21_0.text: When Power Gladiator is destroyed, I get to draw a card!

V0209_09_00_22_0.text: By Synchro Summoning, Hyper Librarian lets me draw a card!

V0209_09_00_23_0.text: By discarding a card, Blade Blaster negates a Spell or Trap!

V0209_09_00_24_1.text: I banish a T.G. from my Graveyard to banish this card!

V0209_09_00_25_0.text: Blade Blaster returns to my field during the Standby Phase!

V0209_09_00_26_0.text:
Halberd Cannon!
Stop that monster from being summoned!

V0209_09_00_27_0.text: Halberd Cannon may be gone, but another T.G. replaces it!

V0209_09_00_28_0.text: T.G. Halberd Cannon/Assault Mode's effect activates!

V0209_09_00_28_1.text: That monster's banished, as are your Special Summoned ones!

V0209_09_00_29_0.text: When this card is destroyed, I can revive Halberd Cannon!

V0209_09_00_30_0.text: Star Guardian lets me retrieve a T.G. from my Graveyard!

V0209_09_00_31_0.text: Star Guardian Special Summons a T.G. from my hand!

V0209_09_00_32_0.text: I'll show you what lies beyond the edges of reality!

V0209_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0209_37_00_00_0.text:
Remove Level 2 limiter!
Open regulators!
Navigation is a go!

V0209_37_00_01_0.text:
Remove Level 5 limiter!
Launch boosters!
Systems are go!

V0209_37_00_02_0.text:
Flight control!
Remove Level 5 limiter!
Boosters at 120%!

V0209_37_00_02_1.text:
Recovery network fixed!
All systems are go!
Synchro Summon!

V0209_37_00_03_0.text:
Remove Level 5 limiter!
Open regulators!
Uplink is a go!

V0209_37_00_04_1.text:
Remove Level 10 limiter!
Main booster controls are a go!

V0209_37_00_04_2.text:
Step out of the shadows and into the light!
Accel Synchro!

V0209_37_00_05_1.text:
Remove max limiter!
Open regulators!
All systems are go!

V0209_37_00_05_2.text:
Infinite power will create a new future!
Go! Delta Accel!

V0209_37_00_06_0.text:
Remove Level 5 limiter!
Open regulators!
All systems are go!

V0209_13_00_21_0.text: I Special Summon a T.G. Token!

V0209_19_00_15_0.text:
T.G. Power Gladiator!
Show the might of your axe!

V0209_28_00_00_0.text: Your insecurities are slamming the brakes on your Duel.

V0209_28_00_01_0.text: You can't keep up with my Dueling.

V0209_28_00_02_0.text: Since I surpassed my limits, you're no match for me.

V0209_28_00_03_0.text: You can't win unless you Duel with conviction!

V0209_28_00_04_0.text: This is the power beyond Synchro!

V0209_28_00_05_0.text:
What's wrong, Yusei?
Your fear is holding you back!

V0209_28_00_06_0.text: The future is heading in a new direction.

V0209_28_00_06_1.text: A direction that my friends and I are creating!

V0209_29_00_00_0.text: I can’t reveal all my Accel Synchro secrets to you.

V0209_29_00_01_0.text: I knew there was something special about you.

V0209_29_00_02_0.text: You have great potential to do amazing things.

V0209_29_00_03_0.text: I'm looking forward to Dueling you again.

V0209_29_00_04_0.text: Yusei, you're my hope for a better future.

V0209_29_00_04_1.text: A future that shines brighter than my Accel Synchro!

V0209_29_00_05_0.text: Yusei, you proved why I believe in you.

V0209_29_00_06_0.text: So this is your true strength...

V0209_29_00_08_0.text:
Aporia...
I feel such sadness from you...

V0209_29_00_09_0.text:
Z-one...
Is it really impossible to save you?

V0209_33_00_00_0.text: I'll show you what's beyond the beyond!

V0209_33_00_02_0.text: Can you keep up with me?

V0209_30_00_01_0.text: Are you daring me to make a move?

V0209_30_00_02_0.text: I was starting to get bored going easy on you.

V0209_34_00_01_0.text: I can't believe you achieved that combo!

V0209_34_00_02_0.text: You showed me that you have great potential.

V0209_34_00_03_0.text: So you do have the courage to transcend your limits!

V0209_34_00_04_0.text: I think that card is a bluff.

V0209_34_00_05_0.text: You dare interfere with my Accel Synchro!

V0209_34_00_07_0.text:
Synchronicity is the key.
A clear mind.

V0209_34_00_08_0.text: Nothing can chain me down! Top Clear Mind!

V0209_35_00_00_0.text: I take Synchro Summoning to a whole new level!

V0209_36_00_00_0.text: I leave the rest to you!

V0209_36_00_01_0.text: Can't wait to see how you Duel.

V0209_36_00_02_0.text: Sorry about this, but I know you can handle it!

V0209_26_00_00_0.text: I now realize how strong you are...
